    </div>
    <div class = "column-2">
        <h3 class="my-secondary-title">A real online shopping experience!</h3>
        <p>Scroll through your store, add to cart, and submit your order.</p>
        <img class="photo" src="\images\screenshot.png">
    </div>
</div>